---
title: Chicken Breasts, Lentil and Goat Cheese Salad with Herbs and Walnuts
description: Satisfying and sophisticated, this chicken salad makes a superb supper. Marinated lentils provide a hearty base and creamy, tangy goat cheese is rolled in fresh herbs for a luxurious topping.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/HF_Y24_R1018_W22_CA_RV154646-6_Main_low-0110c77f.jpg
